# =============================================================================
# Full-package deploy exclusions (sf project deploy start --source-dir force-app)
# =============================================================================
# When metadata references an object, field, or BRE artifact that is missing or
# special in a target org, we EXCLUDE it here rather than adding dependencies to
# the repo without an explicit product/architecture decision.
#
# Before removing a line: ensure the dependency exists in this package (or the
# org is intentionally the source of truth) and full deploy is re-verified.
# Before adding new exclusions: prefer fixing real drift; document the reason.
# Do NOT add net-new CustomObject / Apex to the repo just to silence deploy
# errors without stakeholder approval.
# =============================================================================

# BRE: cannot deploy over an active expression-set version. Deactivate in Setup
# (or retrieve/merge from org) before dropping this line.
**/CommunicationDispatchResolver.expressionSetDefinition-meta.xml
**/CoreGateScreenVisibilityResolver.expressionSetDefinition-meta.xml
**/OnboardingOrchestrator_V2.expressionSetDefinition-meta.xml

# Email: target org missing folder Approval_Process (or folder API name mismatch).
**/email/Approval_Process/**

**/jsconfig.json
**/.eslintrc.json
**/.DS_Store
